Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.56,0:01:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Straw Hats were searching for Vegapunk\Nwho vanished.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, further anomalies occurred\Nin the Labophase.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stella! Come on out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stella?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,An explosion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Respond! What was that explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Pythagoras?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The video feeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...are going off one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Usopp and the others found\NPythagoras who got blown up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Incomprehensible!\NThe Seraphim's Rebellion!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Love-Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...Mellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,York!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Seraphim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Seraphim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,W... Why are you moving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the best brain in the world, right?!\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't listen to me, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a laser beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you wanted to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna fight to the bitter end,\NI'll go along with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you targeting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your aim sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you came to fight me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it was arrogant of me to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they our enemies now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They started attacking out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain it to me, Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. All right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...kick their asses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the Seraphim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll test the rank of authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Hawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:07:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is commanding you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how you stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They came after CP-0, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna let these fools die cuffed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because it'd leave a sour aftertaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not listening to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't obey our orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hover!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your Dom Shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught a glimpse of heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working!\NCommunications are out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she'd obey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I fight back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't someone you can defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's our creation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The strongest form of humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a really troubling situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not following my orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's one of the Vegapunks\Nwho is commanding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the communication failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...and this situation of\Nbeing trapped in the barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:31.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,GOOD
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...were all calculated?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That means somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...wants to kill us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill us all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Seraphim...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Straw Hat and Roronoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we make a truce...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...and form a temporary alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you uncuff us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'd find us useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They look disgusted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:13:00.78,On Top,,0,0,0,,INSIDE THE LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me... food...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been two months...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...without decent food...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we gonna die in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:25.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,WORLD GOVERNMENT INTELLIGENCE AGENCIES\NCP5, CP7, AND CP8
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Two months ago,\Nafter we investigated Egghead,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we left the island\Nbut were attacked by the Sea Beast Weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So we headed back to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The other Cipher Pol agents\Nwho came to investigate our disappearance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...all ended up here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I thought you were the mastermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I didn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...this was happening on Egghead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It sure was strange...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is no way\Nthat research on the Ponegliffs...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...could be leaked to the Government.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naval Branch G-9, the ships set out!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:08.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,NAVY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The number of vessels, large and small,\Nheaded for Egghead exceeds 100 now!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you, get off the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:43.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,FABIRIO, EGGHEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Sentomaru-{\i1}san{\i}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is happening on the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you deploy the Pacifistas\Nall over the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, an island called Ohara...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...suddenly disappeared from the world map.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they rebelled\Nagainst the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ohara Incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Ohara Incident.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It took place on the island of Ohara,\Nhome to the world's largest historical library.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Scholars and residents\Nwho attempted to decipher the Ponegliffs...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...which was forbidden by the Government...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...were killed in a Naval bombardment.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only a single girl survived.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nico Robin.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that Old Man Punk, who has\Nthe best brain in the world, is being targeted...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...means they contemplated all the losses...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...but still decided that he should be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, a worse incident\Nthan the one at Ohara...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...could happen here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening up there now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say we uncuff you guys\Nand fight together with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd just let us cuff you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we get over the crisis together...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we submit to you cuffing us again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Then we'll uncuff you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That was obviously bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...Baldy's technique?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dice-Dice Fruit power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:02.24,On Top,,0,0,0,,ONE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:21.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doredake hashitte kita noka{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:28.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wakaranai mama kizuato kazoeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:35.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zutto atama no naka ni aru takara no chizu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:42.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mirai wo sagashi tsuzuketeru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:49.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hontou no yakusoku wa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real promise{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:56.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mune no oku no motto oku ni aru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:21:05.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dare mo mina oitsukenai yume{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:21:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream that no one can catch up with{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:11.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitotsu dakishimete{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:18.27,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}taiyou no youni warau anata e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:25.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ano hi to onaji uta wo utau yo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:32.24,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}otona ni nattemo wasuretakunai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget even when I grow up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:39.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kono negai ga todoku made{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dive into the Sea of Information!\NThe Punk Records Library!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Lilith, one of the Satellites of\NDr. Vegapunk, the genius scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Edison, also Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll introduce this one!\NDracule Mihawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a former member of the Seven Warlords\Nand the world's strongest swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With a swing of the Black Blade "Night,"\None of the Supreme Grade Swords,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.78,0:22:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,he can slash anything into two!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born on March 9th\Nand likes red wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many years it takes, I will hold\Nthis seat of the strongest and wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to surpass me! Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He and Shanks had a longstanding duel\Nback in the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,which apparently has never been settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,His residence was a deserted castle\Nin the ruins of the Muggy Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Paramount War,\Nat the request of Zoro who was sent flying there,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mihawk gave him training in swordsmanship\Nfor two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.69,0:22:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,While Luffy and the others were in a fierce fight\Nagainst the Emperors of the Sea, Kaido and Big Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the abolition of the Seven Warlords system put him\Nin the position of being hunted by the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So he joined forces with Crocodile and became\Na member of a new organization, Cross Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a row about Buggy becoming\Nthe head of the organization before they knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.21,0:23:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Will someone emerge to threaten\Nhis position as the strongest swordsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.01,0:23:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.59,0:23:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.30,0:23:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen it,\Ndonate to our research fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro{\i1}-san{\i}, we'll feature the great pirates\Nwho rule the New World, the Four Emperors of the Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter who is an Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just beat the hell out of anyone\Nand make our captain the King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece! "Making History!\NThe Turbulent Old and New Four Emperors!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy's gonna become the King of the Pirates!
